  <FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questNameRules.rulesStrings.2>任務名稱-&gt;[facility]狀況</FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questNameRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questNameRules.rulesStrings.3>任務名稱-&gt;荒地[facility]恢復</FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questNameRules.rulesStrings.3>
  <FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questNameRules.rulesStrings.4>任務名稱-&gt;戰前[facility]重新激活</FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questNameRules.rulesStrings.4>
